description:
This is a 28 minute workout called '25 Minute Golf Mobility Routine (FOLLOW ALONG)' from the channel Tom Merrick.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

This video shares a golf focused mobility routine that works to improve hip flexibility through the internal and external rotation. It also focuses on spinal rotation and a touch of hamstring / hip flexor flexibility.

See you in the next video!...
